fixnum or bignum or 0 if it is not.

@cindex [RationalP]
@item RationalP (@var{Object})
sets the eq condition code bit to 1 if @var{Object} is a
fixnum, bignum, or ratio or 0 if it is not.

@cindex [FloatP]
@item FloatP (@var{Object})
sets the eq condition code bit to 1 if @var{Object} is a
short-float or long-float or 0 if it is not.

@cindex [NumberP]
@item NumberP (@var{Object})
sets the eq condition code bit to 1 if @var{Object} is a
